      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 2,
      "version": 168,
      "versionNonce": 795492388,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1782628730523,
      "link": null,
      "text": "Requirements\n\nFunctional\n- POST /create-url\n- GET /{short-url}\n\nNon-functional\n- POST: low latency\n- GET: high availability",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 0,
      "lineHeight": 1.2,
      "index": "a1",
      "locked": false,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Requirements\n\nFunctional\n- POST /create-url\n- GET /{short-url}\n\nNon-functional\n- POST: low latency\n- GET: high availability",
      "autoResize": false
    },
    {
      "id": "api",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 423.46420159439367,
      "y": 139.1706379987233,
      "width": 320,
      "height": 215.99999999999997,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#f8f9fa",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 3,
      "version": 125,
      "versionNonce": 1534137244,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1782628743329,
      "link": null,
      "text": "API Contract\n\nPOST /create-url\n- Request: long-url\n- Response: 201 Created\n- Returns short-url\n\nGET /{short-url}\n- Response: 301 Permanent Redirect\n- Redirects to long-url",
      "fontSize": 18,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 0,
      "lineHeight": 1.2,
      "index": "a2",
      "locked": false,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "API Contract\n\nPOST /create-url\n- Request: long-url\n- Response: 201 Created\n- Returns short-url\n\nGET /{short-url}\n- Response: 301 Permanent Redirect\n- Redirects to long-url",
      "autoResize": false
    },
    {
      "id": "data",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 443.48808418183137,
      "y": 414.9831053574968,
      "width": 300,
      "height": 129.6,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#f8f9fa",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 4,
      "version": 371,
      "versionNonce": 1341561764,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1782628730523,
      "link": null,
      "text": "Data Model\n\n- long-url: string\n- short-url: string\n- created-at: timestamp\n- Optional: created-by / expiry",
      "fontSize": 18,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 0,
      "lineHeight": 1.2,
      "index": "a3",
      "locked": false,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Data Model\n\n- long-url: string\n- short-url: string\n- created-at: timestamp\n- Optional: created-by / expiry",
      "autoResize": false
    },
    {
      "id": "design",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 52.97666128422304,
      "y": 584.2352592068944,
      "width": 474.2959812084368,
      "height": 215.99999999999997,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "#f8f9fa",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 1,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 5,
      "version": 274,
      "versionNonce": 2075918884,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1782627566349,
      "link": null,
      "text": "Design Notes\n\n- Short key generation using Base62\n- Alphabet: a-z, A-Z, 0-9 (62 chars)\n- 6 chars gives ~56B combinations; 7 chars gives\n~3.5T\n- Use distributed ID/counter for uniqueness\n- Cache hot mappings in Redis\n- Primary DB for persistence\n- GET uses cache first, DB fallback",
      "fontSize": 18,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "baseline": 0,
      "lineHeight": 1.2,
      "index": "a4",
      "locked": false,
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Design Notes\n\n- Short key generation using Base62\n- Alphabet: a-z, A-Z, 0-9 (62 chars)\n- 6 chars gives ~56B combinations; 7 chars gives ~3.5T\n- Use distributed ID/counter for uniqueness\n- Cache hot mappings in Redis\n- Primary DB for persistence\n- GET uses cache first, DB fallback",
      "autoResize": false
    },
    {
